Package lubiku.castleQuest.Controller.Handlers

Class EventHandler

java.lang.Object
lubiku.castleQuest.Controller.Handlers.EventHandler
public class EventHandler extends Object

EventHandler

The EventHandler class handles events and event collisions in the game. It is responsible for managing event rectangles, checking for events, and handling event interactions.
